{"tid":283582,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜麗文晒線嘟嘴賣萌　網友睇到噴晒血","createTime":"2017-06-14T09:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T01:19:54.000Z","uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"31f22bf278f56e284a29de525981ff770d775626","tid":283582,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T09:20:50.000Z","msg":"夏天將近，唔少明星藝人都去游水消暑，同陽光玩遊戲，就好似歌手姜麗文（Lesley）近日就出外旅遊消暑，佢仲喺社交網上載咗多張喺泳池嘅照片，相中可見，穿上粉紅色三點式嘅Lesley，唔單止微晒事業線，又嘟嘴賣萌，網友都大讚非常可愛，而其中一張相，Lesley仲擺出誘人嘅甫士，展現其美好身段，相當養眼，唔少網友都大讚Lesley身形fit到漏，簡直令人羨慕，有網友亦搞笑留言話睇到鼻血直流，可想而知Lesley嘅威力係幾咁勁呀！<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=ReFw4jtHjuKOjjlGVIrOv0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=07dab2c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>"},{"pid":"9917430566f4fdb4f5e61476d77d0e69b1d7a505","tid":283582,"uid":2170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T09:23:36.000Z","msg":"Post 如其名"},{"pid":"447d92488bed739320ab7e5a7031be0c9a5c7292","tid":283582,"uid":10441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T09:28:04.000Z","msg":"黑仔呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5db7bca2bd1891d766fd5b0fefb2a60f49202b","tid":283582,"uid":107231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T01:19:54.000Z","msg":"歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}